uit.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Katerine\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-body wax\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"his modesty\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"a garland\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"leaves\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"fruit\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to the controversy over his look and The Last Supper segment of the ceremony, Katerine - who describes himself as 'a bit of an exhibitionist' - toldLe Parisien: 'I suffered a lot but I loved it.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"his look\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper segment\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"Katerine\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"an exhibitionist' - toldLe Parisien\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am proud.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's my culture.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my culture\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are full of different people and everyone lives their own way and, above all, has the right to do so.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different people\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"their own way\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I loved doing it.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\":